         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne bot. &amp; zool. Garden, ¶ 31 Aug. 60. ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ I have the honor to solicit, that you will be pleased to permit me expending the sum of eighty pound Sterling, set apart under authority No. 222...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">60.08.31</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To William Nicholson</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Q60/7691, unit 748, VPRS 1189/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne bot. &amp; zool. Garden,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">31 Aug. 60.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to solicit, that you will be pleased to permit me expending the sum of eighty pound Sterling, set apart under authority No. 222 for the payment of small repairs &amp;c, in defraying ordinary wages for gardenwork during this and the following quarter of the year, the pressure of ground-work in this establishment during the season rendering it preferable to postpone some smaller mechanics works, for which the above sum was intended, til a later period.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I beg also to solicit, that the unexpended balance, left from the labor vote under authority C.S. No. 22 &amp;143<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Annotated respectively in another hand, '£63.13.6' and '7/6'.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>amounting to £64. 1. -<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>may be added to the additional labourvote, solicited for on this occasion.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your most obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The honorable the Chief Secretary.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Approval for M's request was annotated to the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>file cover, dated 5 September 1860.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
         </div>
